title: [Market Bend, Black Foot Alley]
description: Well-kept granite residences line both sides of the alley.  Several plainly dressed merchants, each struggling to carry a large crate filled with goods, seem to be slowly and carefully working their way through the mess of pedestrians towards a small alley that breaks off to the west.

Well-kept granite residences line both sides of the alley, their facades illuminated by torches affixed to either side of their doors.  A line of gaunt river rats picks their way through the refuse on the street towards a small alley that breaks off to the west.
